This paper discusses the use of causal modeling and decision analysis in managing intelligent systems for decision making. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE).
